The role of marriage in the causal pathway from economic conditions early in 
life to mortality.

van den Berg GJ(1), Gupta S(2).

Author information:
(1)University of Mannheim, Mannheim, Germany; Institute for Labor Market Policy 
Evaluation (IFAU), Uppsala, Sweden; VU University Amsterdam, Amsterdam, The 
